  </style>

<!-- ============ HEADER (shared shell) ============ -->

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <Svg19 class="botan hero-botan-tl" aria-hidden="true" />
  <Svg20 class="botan hero-botan-br" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Zuo Yue Zi Meal Plan</p>
    <h1>Herbal Meal</h1>
    <p class="cn-title">藥膳月子餐</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">Nourished. Restored. Whole.</p>
    <p class="lede">You've already done the hardest thing your body will ever do. For the next thirty days, every meal and every herbal drink is <em>someone else's job</em> — not yours.</p>
    <p class="hero-price"><span class="from">30 days · 3 meals a day · herbal drinks included</span>{usd(products.local_herbal_30d.price)}</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-primary">See what's included</a>
      <a href="#taste" class="btn btn-ghost">Try a taste first</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- HERO BANNER IMAGE — replace with a wide, warm hero shot of a full Herbal meal spread + the herbal drink (~1600×640) -->
  <div class="hero-banner reveal">
    <div class="img-slot">
      <!-- <img src="images/herbal-hero.jpg" alt="A full Herbal Meal spread — soups, entrée, rice, vegetables and the warm herbal drink"> -->
      <span class="slot-icon">❀</span>
      <span class="slot-label">Hero Image</span>
      <span class="slot-hint">Wide shot of a full Herbal meal spread with the herbal drink · ~1600 × 640</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ OPENING ============ -->
<section class="opening">
  <div class="narrow reveal">
    <p>If you're looking at our plans and wondering whether the herbal drinks are really worth it — whether the meals alone would do — it's a fair question. Plenty of mothers ask it.</p>
    <p>Here's the honest answer. The meals feed you. The herbal drinks are the other half of Zuo Yue Zi — the daily ritual your grandmother would have insisted on, brewed from formulas that change as the weeks change. Doing it yourself means sourcing herbs, watching a pot, and remembering which formula belongs to which day. With a newborn on your chest, at 2 a.m., that is not a small ask.</p>
    <p class="pull">So we kept the tradition whole: someone else cooks, someone else brews, and you simply recover.</p>
    <p>The Herbal Meal plan is our most complete program — three warm, cooked-from-scratch Zuo Yue Zi meals a day, <em>plus</em> the JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink for all thirty days, included. No prepping. No sourcing. No Googling "what should I eat after birth" at midnight. Just the whole tradition, delivered fresh to your door.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ DAILY ============ -->
<section class="daily" id="daily">
  <Svg22 class="botan daily-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Arrives Every Day</p>
      <h2>The whole tradition, without the hassle</h2>
      <p>Every day of your thirty days, you'll enjoy:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="daily-grid reveal">
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a warming soup / broth dish (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A warming soup or broth · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>一</span></div>
          <h3>Three comforting meals</h3>
          <p>Balanced the traditional way to restore strength, energy, and gut health — soups, slow braises, gentle vegetables, and nourishing rice dishes, in the sequence your recovery follows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — the daily herbal drink, warm in a cup (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Herbal Drink</span><span class="slot-hint">The warm daily herbal drink · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>二</span></div>
          <h3>The herbal drinks — included</h3>
          <p>The JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink, brewed for you and arriving with your meals. Formulas that have anchored Chinese postpartum care for generations, staged across the month instead of poured the same way every day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a neatly plated daily meal set (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A plated daily meal set · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>三</span></div>
          <h3>A nourishing rhythm</h3>
          <p>Breakfast, lunch, dinner, and your drink — arriving like clockwork so your body feels seen, supported, and steady, even on the days when everything else feels upside down.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ GALLERY ============ -->
<section class="gallery" id="gallery">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">On the Table</p>
      <h2>A look at the food</h2>
      <p>Real dishes — and the daily drink — from an Herbal week.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid reveal">
      <!-- IMAGE — hero dish, tall (~800×880) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Feature Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">Tall hero dish · ~800 × 880</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="gallery-note">Menus and formulas rotate across the thirty days to follow the recovery sequence.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PERSONA ============ -->
<section class="persona">
  <Svg23 class="botan persona-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="persona-grid reveal">
      <div class="persona-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Perfect For You If…</p>
        <h2>You want the tradition kept whole.</h2>
        <p>The Herbal Meal is for the mom who doesn't want to piece it together — meals and herbal drinks, arriving as one plan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-right">
        <p>Maybe you did the meals alone the first time and always wondered about the drinks. Or your mother did the full month and you'd like the same for yourself — without asking her to stand over a pot at seventy.</p>
        <p>Maybe you grew up hearing about Zuo Yue Zi and you're balancing tradition with modern life — you want the herbs sourced, brewed, and handed to you warm, not one more thing to research. Or maybe you simply want to feel <em>nourished, cared for, and less overwhelmed</em>.</p>
        <p>Whatever your journey, this plan exists so you can receive the whole tradition — and rest inside it, fully present with your baby.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ QUOTE ============ -->
<section class="quote-band">
  <div class="stamp-wm" style="top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
  <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
  <div class="quote-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Moms Say</p>
    <p class="q">"The drinks were the part I would've skipped, and the part I'd never skip again. It felt like someone had thought of everything before I could worry about it."</p>
    <p class="by">— An Herbal Meal mom</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ADD-ONS ============ -->
<section class="addons" id="addons">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Make It Yours</p>
      <h2>Two ways to go deeper</h2>
      <p>Your herbal drinks are already included. These add-ons are here if you want more.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="addon-grid reveal">
      <div class="addon-card">
        <!-- IMAGE — a cup of chicken essence (~760×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Add-on Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A cup of chicken essence · ~760 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="addon-body">
          <p class="tag">Recovery Booster</p>
          <h3>Slow-Simmered Chicken Essence</h3>
          <p class="cn">熬雞精</p>
          <p>Your go-to recovery booster — slowly simmered for hours from <strong>aged hens and white-feather chickens</strong> until every drop is rich with collagen, protein, and minerals, then concentrated into one small, warming cup.</p>
          <p>Easy to sip on the days you're too tired for a full meal, it arrives ready to warm — no cooking, no cleanup. Mothers who add it tend to keep it for the whole month.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.chicken_essence.price)} / serving · add on whenever you like</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="addon-card">
        <!-- IMAGE — Sheng Hua Tang, warm in a cup (~760×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Add-on Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">Sheng Hua Tang, warm in a cup · ~760 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="addon-body">
          <p class="tag">First-Week Add-On</p>
          <h3>Sheng Hua Tang</h3>
          <p class="cn">生化湯</p>
          <p>The classical first-week formula, traditionally taken in the earliest days after birth — the one your elders would have handed you before anything else.</p>
          <p>Add it by the day alongside your plan, or take the ready-made 7-day course and have the whole first week settled at once.</p>
          <p class="addon-price">{usd(products.herbal_drink.price)} / day · or a ready-made 7-day course, {usd(products.herbal_drink.price * 7)}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PRICING ============ -->
<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <Svg24 class="botan pricing-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Choose Your Length</p>
      <h2>One plan, your timeline</h2>
      <p>Three warm meals a day plus your herbal drinks, delivered fresh daily. Pick the length that fits your recovery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="price-grid reveal">
      <div class="price-card">
        <p class="mode">Every Day Includes</p>
        <h3>Herbal Meal</h3>
        <p class="cn">藥膳月子餐</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Breakfast</strong> — egg &amp; porridge</li>
          <li><strong>Lunch</strong> — fish soup or lunch soup, entrée, vegetables, rice &amp; grains</li>
          <li><strong>Dinner</strong> — Taiwanese postpartum soup, dinner soup, entrée, vegetables, rice &amp; grains</li>
          <li><strong>2 desserts</strong> + a daily healing drink</li>
          <li><strong>JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink (30 days)</strong> — <em>included, not an add-on</em></li>
          <li>Warm, cooked-from-scratch Zuo Yue Zi dishes, delivered fresh daily</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={orderUrl('local_herbal', locale)} class="btn btn-primary">Order online</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <p class="mode">Pricing</p>
        <h3>By Length</h3>
        <p class="cn">依天數計費</p>
        <div class="tier-row feat"><span class="d">30 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_herbal_30d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">21 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_herbal_21d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">14 Days</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_herbal_14d.price)}</span></div>
        <div class="tier-row"><span class="d">1 Day</span><span class="p">{usd(products.local_herbal_1d.price)}</span></div>
        <p class="dep">14–30 day plans: {usd(deposits.herbal)} deposit · balance within 3 days of first delivery. 1-day: paid in full.</p>
        <a href={orderUrl('local_herbal', locale)} class="btn btn-ghost">Order online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="pricing-foot">Not sure which length fits? Call us at <a href={`tel:${phones.main}`}>{phoneDisplay(phones.main)}</a> — we're happy to talk it through, no pressure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ DOWNLOADS (shared block — reuse on every product page) ============ -->
<section class="actions" id="resources">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Review At Your Own Pace</p>
      <h2>Download the details</h2>
      <p>Prefer to look things over on your own? Grab the order form, compare every plan side by side, or browse the full menu.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="action-downloads reveal">
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Main_Order_Form.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg25 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Order Form <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">下載訂購單</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Meal_Comparison_Chart.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg26 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Meal Comparison Chart <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">餐點對照表</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://file.jingmommy.com/f/Menu.pdf" class="action-btn">
        <Svg27 class="ico" />
        <span class="lbl"><span class="en">Full Menu <span class="pdf-tag">PDF</span></span><span class="cn">菜單</span></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ INCLUDED BAND (Herbal is the top tier — no upsell) ============ -->
<section class="upgrade">
  <div class="upgrade-inner reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Nothing Left to Add</p>
    <h2>The herbal drinks are already yours</h2>
    <p>This is the complete plan. Every meal, and the JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink for all thirty days — brewed, staged, and delivered with your food. There is no upgrade from here, and nothing left for you to arrange.</p>
    <a href={orderUrl('local_herbal', locale)} class="btn btn-primary">Order online — from {usd(products.local_herbal_1d.price)} a day</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<section class="faq-band" id="faq">
  <Svg28 class="botan faq-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Good Questions</p>
      <h2>Before you decide</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are the herbal drinks included, or do I add them on?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Included. The JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink comes with the Herbal Meal plan for the full 30 days — brewed for you and delivered alongside your meals. It's the reason this plan exists, and there is nothing extra to arrange or pay for.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What's the difference between Herbal and Classic?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Think of them as two halves of the same tradition. Both plans bring the same three meals a day from the same kitchen — the food that does the rebuilding: warm soups, proteins, gentle vegetables, staged to your recovery.</p><p>The Herbal Meal adds the other half — the JingMommy Postpartum Herbal Drink, every day for the full thirty days, included. These aren't one drink repeated; they're a sequence of formulas that changes as your body moves through the weeks — the inner side of Zuo Yue Zi that food alone doesn't reach. Sourcing the herbs and knowing which formula belongs to which week is the hard part, and on this plan it's already brewed and delivered with your meals, so you never have to think about it.</p><p>So the real question isn't the price — it's how much you want handled for you. Choose the Herbal Meal if you'd like the whole tradition taken care of; choose Classic if you'd rather have the meals now and add the herbal drinks by the day whenever you like, at {usd(products.herbal_drink.price)}/day.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do the herbal drinks taste bitter?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We'd rather be straight with you: a few can. Mothers tell us a couple of the formulas carry a stronger, more bitter herbal note, while most of the rest go down easily. We won't pretend every cup is delicious — but no formula stays for long. The drinks change every couple of days as your body moves through the stages of recovery, so even one you don't love is behind you within a day or two. Zuo Yue Zi is about healing first; how it tastes comes second.</p><p>One thing to note: our sample days don't include the herbal drinks — those are brewed for after birth and staged by week, so they aren't part of a tasting.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How does delivery work?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>In our regular service area, meals are delivered fresh every day and we aim to reach your door before noon — though actual times can shift with traffic and routes, so an exact hour isn't guaranteed. Remote areas receive every-other-day delivery, delivery times there can't be guaranteed, and an additional delivery fee may apply. Refrigerate your meals when they arrive, and heat them thoroughly before eating.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>When should I order, and how does payment work?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>At least one month before your due date, if you can. The week your baby arrives, you will not have the bandwidth to compare plans or fill out forms — and you shouldn't have to. Your start date can be adjusted once the baby comes.</p><p>The 14, 21, and 30-day plans take an <strong>{usd(deposits.herbal)} deposit</strong> at booking, with the balance due within 3 days of first delivery. The 1-day plan is paid in full, with no deposit.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

